There are test scripts which will give you feedback as far as pass fail.  Submission tests are more thorough, but project descriptions will tell you what's required.  Grading will be done in the background and will not be available immediately.

elements.text: There are test scripts which will give you feedback as far as pass fail.  Submission tests are more thorough, but project descriptions will tell you what's required.  Grading will be done in the background and will not be available immediately.

text: There will be two places to submit code: A gradescope TESTING environment and a final SUBMISSION environment.  You can correct mistakes and resubmit an unlimited number of times in the TESTING environment.  The SUBMISSION environment will be limited.
